<P>Being the <HI>Anniver&s;ary</HI> for the ELECTION of His Maje&s;ty's COUNCIL for the Province.</P>
<P>BY EBENEZER PEMBERTON, A. M.</P>
<P>Pa&s;tor of a Church in BOSTON.</P>
