<P>THAT JACOB WENDELL and SAMUEL WATTS, E&s;q^r^s^. be a Committee to wait on the Reverend Mr. EBENEZER PEMBERTON, and return him the Thanks of this Board for his Sermon preached Ye&s;terday be|fore the General Court, being the Anni|ver&s;ary Election of Councellors for this Province; and to de&s;ire a Copy thereof for the Pre&s;s.</P>
